            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, return the pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, crumble your <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> roughly into the pan with your hands and cook for 3-4 min or until caramelised</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>soy sauce</strong> (save the rest for later!) to the pan and cook for 30 secs further</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1620663389185-x200.jpg",
