            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1620663389185-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mushrooms are cooking, add the <strong>remaining soy sauce</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar </strong>and <strong>peanut butter </strong>to the <strong>chilli oil</strong></p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> sauce</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s] </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1620663403328-x200.jpg",
