          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1620663403328-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the noodles are done, add a splash of the<strong> starchy noodle water</strong> to the <strong>sauce</strong> – this is your <strong>Sichuan-style chilli sauce</strong></p><p>Tip: You want the sauce to be a single cream consistency so it can coat all of the noodles!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1620663419510-x200.jpg",
