            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1620663419510-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>Sichuan-style chilli sauce</strong> to the bottom of your serving bowl</p><p>Serve the <strong>drained noodles</strong> on top with the <strong>caramelised mushrooms</strong>, <strong>grated carrot </strong>and <strong>sliced sugar snap peas</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Before eating, toss the noodles and veg through the <strong>Sichuan-style chilli sauce</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
